Class GraphicalObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • gerberFileReader.GraphicalObject
  • public class GraphicalObject
extends java.lang.Object
    A class for representing Gerber graphical objects
    See Also:
    Section 2.3 of the Gerber Layer Format Specification

      Gets the polarity of this GraphicalObject, either DARK (meaning the object should plot on top of and block any other existing objects beneath it in the image) or CLEAR (meaning the object should clear all other existing objects beneath it in the image)
